    "165346385457f0044f": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1653463854c4d6293d-0": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<h2><strong>THE SMART CHOICE</strong></h2>",
            "title_underline_style": "none"
          }
        },
        "1653463854c4d6293d-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For over a decade, Fuelab has pushed technology and innovation forward, manufacturing the most innovative fuel systems found anywhere. At the center of this development, our Prodigy line of brushless fuel pumps were born. Efficient, high-flow fuel pumps designed to handle multiple fuels and pressures, all while holding up to the toughest run conditions enthusiasts can throw at us.</p><p>At Fuelab, we strive for perfection and results. Put your trust in the company that introduced brushless fuel pump technology over 15 years ago and continues to lead the way. You'll be glad you did.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1653463854c4d6293d-0",
        "1653463854c4d6293d-1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/F198651253_3c065068-cc88-4084-bb22-3ea37fc2b1e3.png",
        "overlay_opacity": 0,
        "color_palette": "scheme-1",
