        "text_position": "text-start",
        "width": "boxed",
        "spacing_desktop": 50,
        "spacing_mobile": 30,
        "fix_zindex": 0
      }
    },
    "16534638377c7920c1": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1653463837107b96d3-0": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<h2><strong>FUELING YOUR PASSION</strong></h2>",
            "title_underline_style": "none"
          }
        },
        "1653463837107b96d3-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>What drives you? What is your passion? Well if it's winning races, off-road adventure, street/strip performance, or just making horsepower, you're at the right place for your fueling needs! Our brushless fuel pump technology, along with our extensive line of fuel pressure regulators, filters and systems will feed your engine and keep it running at its best.</p><p>Racers who use Fuelab products report unrivaled reliability and efficiency - they just plain work. We build the best so you can keep doing what you love.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "1653463837107b96d3-0",
        "1653463837107b96d3-1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/F198651253_3c065068-cc88-4084-bb22-3ea37fc2b1e3.png",
